Ever find yourself pondering life’s little (or big) mysteries? Well, here’s one we get a lot when it comes to our natural deodorants:

“Are your sticks and pastes just twins in disguise, or more like distant cousins?”

Spoiler alert: They’re definitely not twins! While they might share some of the same ingredients, that’s where the similarities end.

Swipe through for the key differences 👉 

And if you swipe all the way through to the end, you'll reveal a fun little FREE gift 😍
